  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK983">
<l>aṉpunā ṇoppuravu kaṇṇōṭṭam vāymaiyo</l>
<l>ṭaintucāl pūṉṟiya tūṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Affection, fear (of sin), benevolence, favour and truthfulness; these are the five pillars on which perfect goodness rests.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
